 hyperbolic.\n  Finally, as a consequence of the main results, we answer a few open\nquestions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 16:50:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Aug 2017 20:44:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 28 Oct 2017 04:40:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-31"}
