al resolution is supported on decompositions\nof Euclidean space coming from the theory of tropical hyperplane arrangements.\nThis leads to combinatorial interpretations of the Betti numbers of these\nideals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Aug 2017 22:50:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2017 21:31:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 04:47:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2018 02:08:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-18"}
