f about two is found for the ratio T_(cmf}/Tc,\nand we conjecture that this arises because a band with a small Fermi energy not\nseen in the tunneling results plays a part in increasing T_{cmf}/Tc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Aug 2017 15:41:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 15:55:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-21"}
